TEXT.S: Cliff Barker nalecuhan i Atlanta, Georgia, nanu syubay kanas-mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput. Cliff Barker i 1949 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 5 ku uwac, namapili' tu nu Washington Capitols putiput. 2 bulad 15 demiad, 1921 a mihca, Cliff Barker, miunduay. (mapatay i 1998 a mihca)
